{"about_the_game":"<strong>Drone Warfare</strong> is an action focused flight sim and tower defense hybrid set in the near future.<br><br>Being the newest recruit to <strong>Project Helix</strong>, you are tasked with protecting the last honey bee colonies as they near extinction. Failure is not an option as depleting crops and widening food shortages are threatening humanity.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/DW_Drone.gif?t=1737373363\" /><br><br>You are the remote pilot of the <strong>H-BEE 01 Drone Prototype</strong>, a tiny military flying machine that resembles a honey bee itself. Utilising nano-technology the drone packs an array of powerful weapons and advanced systems for the mission ahead.<br><br>The H-BEE drone is a last ditch attempt to protect what's left of the bee species. Can the dire situation be reversed somehow? And what exactly caused them to disappear in the first place?<br><br><strong><u>Features</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stunning environments for you to explore from an insect's eye view.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/DW_Nest.gif?t=1737373363\" /><br><br></li><li>A diverse set of missions covering recon, defense, interception, and all out war!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/DW_Turret.gif?t=1737373363\" /><br><br></li><li>Deploy over-the-top weaponry and turrets to wreak havoc as you protect the bees from overwhelming odds.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/DW_Attack.gif?t=1737373363\" /><br><br></li><li>Complex flight mechanics that can be adjusted to suit your playing style.</li></ul><br><strong><u>Gameplay</u></strong><br>Although action focused, Drone Warfare also includes the following gameplay features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tower defense elements. Observe enemy patterns and setup turrets around the environment to counter them.<br></li><li>Extensive research and upgrade options for the turrets, your drone, and the bee's themselves.<br></li><li>Full campaign story with vocal narrative.<br></li><li>Dynamic soundtrack.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/DW_FireLogo.gif?t=1737373363\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737373363","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/page.bg.jpg?t=1737373363","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737373363","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737373363","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<strong>Drone Warfare</strong> is an action focused flight sim and tower defense hybrid set in the near future.<br><br>Being the newest recruit to <strong>Project Helix</strong>, you are tasked with protecting the last honey bee colonies as they near extinction. Failure is not an option as depleting crops and widening food shortages are threatening humanity.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/647660/extras/DW_Drone.gif?t=1737373363\" /><br><br>You are the remote pilot of the <strong>H-BEE 01 Drone Prototype</strong>, a tiny military flying machine that resembles a honey bee itself. Utilising nano-technology the drone packs an array of powerful weapons and advanced systems for the mission ahead.<br><br>The H-BEE drone is a last ditch a